	<text_base_description>Privately gated, this new Contemporary Farmhouse offers a stunning retreat in the heart of the iconic Beverly Grove. With over 5,000 sq. ft. of exquisite craftmanship and designer aesthetic, this 5 bed, 6 bath home offers an open floor plan with Chef's kitchen complete with Sub-Zero and Wolf appliances, a theater and wine room, and a spacious office/gym. The main level opens up to a private garden with a pool and spa accentuated by a waterfall and cozy fireplace. The expansive owner's suite comes replete with a luxurious bath, walk-in closet, and private balcony. An entertainer's roof-top deck offers an outdoor kitchen with city and mountain views, including a full view of the Hollywood sign. This smart home features Control4 home automation, Tri-zone climate control, and a 2-car garage.  </text_base_description>
